    "name": "Rogue Zodiacs",
    "steam_appid": 3054470,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rogue Zodiacs is a content-rich, turn-based roguelite hero/team builder with infinite replayability.</strong> In this game, none of your runs will ever feel the same! This game will challenge your adaptability skills. With <strong>3 game modes</strong>, <strong>Adventure</strong> <strong>Mode</strong>, <strong>Survival Mode</strong>, and <strong>Endless Mode</strong>, you need to find the best builds using the resources that you currently have.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TLDR</strong>: This game has...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemy Diversity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run Diversity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Diversity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build Diversity</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras/0d1542427895778ea5a821d48943a8b2.avif?t=1751044251\" width=692 height=146 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A party of<strong> 4 heroes</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 3 of which have <strong>54 unique abilities</strong> each in their own pool.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 1 special hero whose <strong>abilities must be stolen</strong> from enemies you encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- This special hero can steal up to <strong>90 unique abilities</strong>!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras/6b3669053aa714d2275b4b27397aacc1.avif?t=1751044251\" width=692 height=146 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200+ <strong>unique Relics</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Relics are the source of your character's passive powers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>Reliquary</strong> that allows you to <strong>complete your relic collection</strong> by permanently unlocking some after each run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character can equip up to 10 Relics! That's 40 Relics to equip in total!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras/5227d977762c57f9e45072a36febdab8.avif?t=1751044251\" width=692 height=146 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >75+ <strong>unique </strong>enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>12 Zodiacs</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemy variety at its finest. All enemies, including the Zodiacs, have their <strong>own unique set of passive and active abilities</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They all <strong>evolve</strong>, growing stronger the further you go; <strong>unlocking new</strong> passive/active abilities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras/d69e3d7a393777b94e5a4482d3033188.avif?t=1751044251\" width=692 height=146 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 <strong>Locations</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45+ <strong>Hazards.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Location mods that affect <strong>all enemies and allies</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Can be beneficial depending on your situation, but most of the time they are hazardous.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras/0cf7ba51de3451d1c35a593bbc36f975.avif?t=1751044251\" width=692 height=146 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45 levels of <strong>Star Marks</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Adventure <strong>perks </strong>that improve your future runs but not drastically; they're totally optional.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>600+ Status Effects</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- </strong>Many deep mechanics such as on-hit, on-crit, and many various conditional effects.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras/3d05ac9df04a792f8a499f1f5fa0e8e5.avif?t=1751044251\" width=692 height=146 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Abilities are tied</strong> to the Equipments and Weapons equipped.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 45 different <strong>Equipments</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 36 different <strong>Weapons</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combine </strong>duplicates to <strong>upgrade to a higher tier</strong>!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras/859e6933fe99edb8c262239f2630cf11.avif?t=1751044251\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras_big/859e6933fe99edb8c262239f2630cf11.avif?t=1751044251 width=800 height=259 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survival Mode</strong> - recently added in 2.0 update.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight hordes of enemies until the Zodiac appears, the final boss.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ARPG-like stat-heavy build-your-own-characters gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every kill, power up with augments, passives, items, special events/effects, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock a total of 162 abilities from first win rewards.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras/57ed6d40d8343f3283b3d23add732893.avif?t=1751044251\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras_big/57ed6d40d8343f3283b3d23add732893.avif?t=1751044251 width=800 height=259 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Mode</strong> - recently added in 3.0 update.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight never-ending waves of evolving enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ultimate limit test to see how far your builds can go.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete! Score as many kills as you can and climb the ladder!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras/8b9b6b5ccff0d3e819f67b509737c374.avif?t=1751044251\" width=692 height=146 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Steam Features</strong>:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 Steam <strong>Achievements</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online Global <strong>Leaderboard </strong>for each game mode; compete with players all over the world!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam <strong>Cloud</strong>; synchronized save files with your other devices.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam <strong>Family Sharing</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054470/extras/147c95093d691cf7d069ed15af2f70b8.avif?t=1751044251\" width=692 height=146 /></span></p>",
